Usage: reclaimArea [-help] [-maintainHold] [-noDeclone] [-noDeleteBuffer]
                   [-noDownsize] [-preCTS] [-prePlace]

-help                                      # Prints out the command usage
-maintainHold                              # Call hold aware reclaim
                                           # (bool, optional)
-noDeclone                                 # skip declone (bool, optional)
-noDeleteBuffer                            # skip buffer deletion
                                           # (bool, optional)
-noDownsize                                # skip downsize (bool, optional)
-preCTS                                    # skip preCTS (bool, optional)
-prePlace                                  # skip prePlace (bool, optional)